title: BoffoBits #6- Guitarist Larry Carlton on going solo and self production.
description: Both music and the record industry were going through big changes in 1982.  Videos, image and drum machines were becoming the norm.  In this latest BoffoBit, Larry describes how he made the transition from session player to Jazz Crusader member to solo artist.
fulltitle: BoffoBits #6- Guitarist Larry Carlton on going solo and self production.
